extendedInfo.description: Shanghai Yuli Machinery and Technology Development Co., Ltd, found in 1999, is a professional manufacturer in flooring machinery and cleaning machinery industry. Adhering to the "quality priority business philosophy, having experienced R&D staffs, professional workers, advanced CNC center and other modern manufacturing equipments, Shanghai Yuli has passed through the ISO9001 quality system certification and CE certification Our MENDEL brand floor grinding machine, multifunctional floor polishing machine, scrubber dryer, vacuum cleaner, diamond pads and stone care powders are well-known products. MENDEL machines are widely used in many floor engineering and maintenance projects such as World Expo, national high-speed railway , airports, office buildings, hotels, supermarkets and have achieved lead market share in China and exported to more than 10 countries. Mr. Dazhou SUN, chairman of YULI Machinery, is the main founder of YULI Machinery and enjoys the titles of outstanding private entrepreneur, vice chairman of stone care industry Committee.
